title: The International Bad Boys Hour Ep 50: Fun Stories With Jon Huck
description: Wow Jon Huck joins the The International Bad Boys Hour and trust me when I tell you he will blow you mind with his insane stories of drug, sex and felony crimes!  Buckle your seat belts because it's about to get crazy in here! Thank you for listening and all of your support. Please let us know what you guys think of the of the episode.
